<!--T:7-->
# Select two edges in a View. The edges should be more or less parallel.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:TechDraw_2LineCenterLine.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_2LineCenterLine|Centerline Between 2 Lines]]}} button.
